skaya]]\n| ---\n| ---\n| [[Russia]]\n| [[Milk]], [[Meat]], [[Wool]]\n| <ref>{{Cite web|title=Pridonskaya goats|publisher=GeoMedia.Top|url=http://geomedia.top/pridonskaya-goats/|accessdate=2 July 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Pygmy goat|Pygmy]]\n| [[File:Pygmy Goats Seattle Zoo.jpg|85px]]\n| African pygmy, American pygmy\n| [[Cameroon]]\n| [[Goat meat|Meat]], [[Milk]], [[Pet]]\n| \n|-\n| [[Pygora goat|Pygora]]\n| [[File:Oregon Zoo White Goat.jpg|85px]]\n| ---\n| [[Oregon City, Oregon|Oregon City]]\n| [[Animal fiber|Fiber]]\n| \n|-\n| [[Pyrenean Goat|Pyrenean]]\n| [[File:Ch\u00e8vre Pyr\u00e9n\u00e9enne.JPG|85px]]\n| ---\n| [[France]] and [[Spain]]\n| [[Goat meat|Meat]], [[Milk]]\n| \n|-\n| Qinshan\n| ---\n| ---\n| [[Jining]]\n| [[Goatskin (material)|Skin]]\n| \n|-\n| Red Boer\n| [[File:Boer goat at Kalakamati Farm 6.jpg|85px]]\n| ---\n| [[South Africa]]\n| [[Goat meat|Meat]], [[Pet]]\n| \n|-\n| Red Mediterranean\n| ---\n| ---\n| [[Syria]]\n| [[Milk]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rossa Mediterranea o Derivata di Siria|publisher=Agraria.org|url=http://www.agraria.org/caprini/derivatadisiria.htm|accessdate=December 23, 2012|language=es}}</ref>\n|-\n|Red Sokoto\n|\n|Maradi Red\n|Nigeria and Niger Republic\n|Meat, Skin, Milk\n|\n|-\n| [[Repartida]]\n| ---\n| ---\n| Northeastern [[Brazil]]\n| [[Goat meat|Meat]]\n| \n|-\n| [[Rove goat|Rove]]\n| [[File:Chevres Rove BdRhone.jpg|85px]]\n| ---\n| [[France]]\n| [[Goat meat|Meat]]\n| \n|-\n| [[Russian White (goat)|Russian White]]\n| [[File:White goat at Rizopolozhensky Convent in Suzdal.jpg|85px]]\n| ---\n| [[Russia]]\n| [[Milk]]\n| \n|-\n| [[Saanen goat|Saanen]]\n| [[File:Saanenziege.jpg|85px]]\n| ---\n| [[Saanen]]\n| [[Milk]]\n| \n|-\n| [[Sable Saanen]]\n| ---\n| ---\n| [[United States]]\n| [[Milk]]\n| \n|-\n|Sahel\n|\n|Sahelian\n|Sahel Belt of Africa \n|Meat\n|\n|-\n| [[Valdostana]]\n| [[File:Razza Valdostana abc2.JPG|85px]]\n| ---\n| [[Italy]]\n| [[meat]], [[milk]]\n|\n|-\n| [[Sahelian Goat|Sahelian]]\n| ---\n| ---\n| [[West Africa]]\n| [